eparation\",\n  \"summary\": \"jakarta.activation-api:2.0.0 is an API-only artifact; common Activation runtime paths such as MailcapCommandMap and MimetypesFileTypeMap reference implementation classes under com.sun.activation.registries that are not present in the API jar, so meaningful coverage of MIME/command mapping needs the matching implementation jar.\",\n  \"deterministic_setup\": [\n    {\n      \"kind\": \"dependency\",\n      \"coordinate\": \"com.sun.activation:jakarta.activation:2.0.0\",\n      \"scope\": \"testImplementation\",\n      \"reason\": \"The API jar POM states it is intended only for compiling and excludes implementation-specific classes. Local inspection shows MailcapCommandMap and MimetypesFileTypeMap fail with NoClassDefFoundError for com.sun.activation.registries.LogSupport unless the matching implementation artifact is on the test classpath.\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"agent_guidance\": \"Use the Jakarta Activation 2.x package namespace (`jakarta.activation.*`), not the pre-2.0 `javax.activation.*` imports. Be aware that adding the implementation jar introduces duplicate `jakarta.activation` classes; keep tests focused on the target API behavior and use local Gradle/Native Image verification as authoritative.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The matching implementation artifact contains both the missing `com.sun.activation.registries` classes and duplicate `jakarta.activation` classes, so classpath ordering could affect which duplicate classes are loaded.\",\n    \"If the workflow intentionally wants to test the API artifact in strict compile-only isolation, tests must avoid runtime paths that instantiate MIME/mailcap registries.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_03b40740252971c9016a416b080bcc8190af901f1ea47adacf\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 718, "output": 871, "cacheRead": 28672, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 30261, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782672126332, "responseId": "resp_03b40740252971c9016a416afec6688190b7198bd27db6d0c3"}}
